to stop mine,

00:09:32.293 --> 00:09:33.926
but he said he'd do it
his own way,

00:09:33.926 --> 00:09:35.260
whatever that meant,

00:09:35.260 --> 00:09:37.960
and I haven't
seen him since.

00:09:37.960 --> 00:09:39.393
I know what he meant.

00:09:39.393 --> 00:09:42.360
My dad wants to stop Leo
without having to fight,

00:09:42.360 --> 00:09:45.393
because that's
what my dad does.

00:09:45.393 --> 00:09:48.493
