any more insight

00:10:22.066 --> 00:10:23.500
than you do
on its meaning.

00:10:23.500 --> 00:10:25.466
What I do know
is that the folder

00:10:25.466 --> 00:10:28.700
contained two files.

00:10:28.700 --> 00:10:30.433
Bet one of 'em was Celina.

00:10:30.433 --> 00:10:32.133
(Declan)
That is correct.

00:10:32.133 --> 00:10:33.833
And as for
the other file...

00:10:33.833 --> 00:10:35.466
Who was it, Declan?

00:10:35.466 --> 00:10:39.066
The other file was on a boy
by the name of Yuri,

00:10:39.066 --> 00:10:40.900
