but by winning it my way!

00:11:50.540 --> 00:11:52.240
No matter what it takes,

00:11:52.240 --> 00:11:55.073
I'll find a way to
bring the old Rin back!

00:11:55.073 --> 00:11:56.806
You will remember,

00:11:56.806 --> 00:12:00.146
