00:12:21.580 --> 00:12:25.580
Time to ice that dragon,
Winter Bell!

00:12:25.580 --> 00:12:26.946
Attack!

00:12:29.646 --> 00:12:32.946
(groaning)
By banishing Tri‐Eyed
Dice from my graveyard,

